{"tid":1191052,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[小小小眾足球] 2019美洲金盃","createTime":"2019-06-07T17:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T09:39:55.000Z","uid":34572,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"89351a704311de68e64bee38b051d5500d5f07e6","tid":1191052,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T17:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/concacaf-production/image/upload/c_fit,dpr_3.0,f_auto,g_center,q_auto,w_730/v1/goldcup-prod/ticketspg_headerV2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fconcacaf-production%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fc_fit%2Cdpr_3.0%2Cf_auto%2Cg_center%2Cq_auto%2Cw_730%2Fv1%2Fgoldcup-prod%2Fticketspg_headerV2&h=a2584c0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.clubs.nfl.com/image/private/t_editorial_landscape_8_desktop_mobile/f_auto/titans/dgbwxx7d6gfhwskmstv5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.clubs.nfl.com%2Fimage%2Fprivate%2Ft_editorial_landscape_8_desktop_mobile%2Ff_auto%2Ftitans%2Fdgbwxx7d6gfhwskmstv5.jpg&h=614192ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n六隊上屆世界盃中北美洲區外圍賽最後一圈嘅參賽國家<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-s3.si.com/s3fs-public/styles/marquee_large_2x/public/2016/09/07/concacaf-hex-teams.jpg?itok=q2jpEHzO\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-s3.si.com%2Fs3fs-public%2Fstyles%2Fmarquee_large_2x%2Fpublic%2F2016%2F09%2F07%2Fconcacaf-hex-teams.jpg%3Fitok%3Dq2jpEHzO&h=0e382738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n＋<br />\n中北美洲國家聯賽外圍賽頭十名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DcNGJv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DcNGJv.png&h=e5d9637f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賽程<br />\n<a href=\"https://thisisours.goldcup.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthisisours.goldcup.org%2F&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8wEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=24fc5ac5\" target=\"_blank\">https://thisisours.goldcup.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n今屆美洲金盃美其名由美國、牙買加、哥斯達黎加三國合辦。但事實上得B組第一輪喺牙買加踢同C組第一輪喺哥斯達黎加踢，之後全部比賽就喺美國踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62cb96e55b4bc5f2af27e0392babd47bec367c8","tid":1191052,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T17:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6682da6cb53e440ce73ffc99ddeec90ff656421","tid":1191052,"uid":106189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T23:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4377d8a36db357f0493103580492e3e4a95b5d29","tid":1191052,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSgVU9G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSgVU9G.png&h=95727a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面用錯圖，呢幅先係update版"},{"pid":"c6cbc95472d8f73ab5cd377a877385fcf128d1c7","tid":1191052,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ff374f474dba2b44e05535ba49c36e46714819","tid":1191052,"uid":106189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a7756f172521927268a6d785feeb51af8e7719","tid":1191052,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5f4794f187649f2c2cd1d622b9d917203b1040","tid":1191052,"uid":106189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/f