sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"隊長咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:07:58.000Z","msg":"古巴運動員奔投美國個案有好多，因為美國法律容許古巴人入境後逗留，並直接取得合法居留權。近日在美國舉行嘅美洲金盃，古巴隊長盧比斯(Yasmany Lopez)，在比賽期間失蹤，古巴領隊文迪路斯其後證實，盧比斯走咗佬。<br />\n<br />\n古巴出席今屆金盃賽形同運桔，首仗狂吞墨西哥7蛋，次仗再食馬提尼克3蛋，兩場夾埋輸10粒未入過1球，文迪路斯表示，盧比斯喺首仗大敗之後已經失蹤，佢話：「呢個係盧比斯嘅決定，同其他人無關，依家大家都知道，球隊陣容不整。」<br />\n<br />\n事實證明，美國居留權比古巴隊長身份更吸引，盧比斯現年31歲，上陣28場入1球，留喺古巴相信好快掛靴，而且古巴足球如同垃圾，反而投奔美國之後，或者會被美職及低級別聯賽吸納，仲有搵食機會。"},{"pid":"03242e7729eba57d8701aa4c895828dce7d43a74","tid":1191052,"uid":203961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca3e269bece34137788ddf3d37ddce387e5c849e","tid":1191052,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa7ba5d3e781b849b1814e097db67bf8bb7c9090","tid":1191052,"uid":23889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f860109b18855741b794f8dc251ae02144371251","tid":1191052,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:07:44.000Z","msg":"基本上開完post之後發生咁多事都冇時間理，唔覺唔覺已經出咗四隊八強<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64913401_1897612853673958_3323002822387040256_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmAYoNitMUGE5XGwPg9GtMgPQce_J1HT7MGKFypQP4E9s2ZCoR_dmBYvOSN3zJdHNc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=3124dd9057d3c4b1c0d55a12ef1fdcac&amp;oe=5DC16D55\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64913401_1897612853673958_3323002822387040256_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmAYoNitMUGE5XGwPg9GtMgPQce_J1HT7MGKFypQP4E9s2ZCoR_dmBYvOSN3zJdHNc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D3124dd9057d3c4b1c0d55a12ef1fdcac%26oe%3D5DC16D55&h=7438bb9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外古巴隊長變節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"